[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1986},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20240413\u002F3177435894\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20240413\u002F3177435894\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20240413\u002F3177435894\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20240413\u002F3177435894\u002F":1961,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20240413\u002F3177435894\u002F":1970},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2024\u002F04\u002F13\u002Fmonorepo-vite-pnpm-vue3-setup\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1943,"date":1944,"description":1945,"extension":84,"lang":1946,"meta":1947,"navigation":1860,"path":1948,"readingMinutes":1949,"seo":1950,"standalone":1951,"stem":1952,"tags":1953,"tldr":1957,"updated":1958,"url":1959,"__hash__":1960},"content\u002F雜談\u002FMonorepo？來聊聊另一種專案管理架構吧！使用-Vite-pnpm-建立-Vue3-Monorepo.md","Monorepo？來聊聊另一種專案管理架構吧！使用 Vite+ pnpm 建立 Vue3 Monorepo","3177435894",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1931},"minimark",[11,20,24,27,31,34,37,42,45,66,73,76,79,223,226,229,240,243,249,252,256,259,262,548,551,554,560,564,567,570,576,579,582,588,591,594,600,603,606,624,627,631,634,667,678,687,690,694,697,736,739,750,753,777,780,801,804,810,813,819,830,988,1013,1016,1148,1164,1167,1182,1210,1213,1216,1426,1440,1571,1589,1592,1604,1610,1617,1635,1652,1656,1659,1676,1679,1692,1695,1701,1704,1772,1780,1783,1804,1807,1902,1905,1908,1917,1927],[12,13,16],"callout",{"title":14,"type":15},"Note","note",[17,18,19],"p",{},"Monorepo 是「Mono（單一）+ Repo（Repository）」的縮寫，意思是把多個專案放在同一個 Git Repository 裡管理，跟「一個專案一個 Repo」的 Monolith 是相對概念。JavaScript 圈最常見的建立方式是 pnpm workspace 搭配 Vite。",[21,22,23],"h2",{"id":23},"前言",[17,25,26],{},"Monorepo 是什麼呢？而這個專案架構又與普通的專案架構有什麼不同呢？剛好最近有相關專案的需求，所以就寫這一篇記錄一下。",[21,28,30],{"id":29},"什麼是-monorepo","什麼是 Monorepo？",[17,32,33],{},"Monorepo 是什麼東西呢？首先這是多個單字的組合，分別是 Mono 與 Repo，Mono 代表單一的意思，而 Repo 則是 Repository 的縮寫，也就是說 Monorepo 代表的是單一的 Repository。",[17,35,36],{},"感覺滿難懂的吧？沒關係，讓我們先講講其他的專案架構，接著我們再來 Monorepo 吧！",[38,39,41],"h3",{"id":40},"monolith-repository單體儲存庫","Monolith Repository（單體儲存庫）",[17,43,44],{},"通常我們在開發專案的時候，都會歷經以下幾個步驟：",[46,47,48,52,60,63],"ul",{},[49,50,51],"li",{},"建立專案",[49,53,54,55,59],{},"初始化版本控制（",[56,57,58],"code",{},"git init","）",[49,61,62],{},"開發功能",[49,64,65],{},"提交變更到遠端儲存庫（GitHub、GitLab、Bitbucket 等）",[17,67,68],{},[69,70],"img",{"alt":71,"src":72},"Repository","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fmonorepo\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202024-04-13%2023.50.43.png",[17,74,75],{},"而這個專案就會獨立一個 Git Repository，也是我們最基本的專案架構，那麼這種架構又稱之為 Monolith Repository（後面僅稱 Monolith），也就是單一專案的 Repository。",[17,77,78],{},"那麼 Monolith 的專案架構可能長這樣：",[80,81,86],"pre",{"className":82,"code":83,"language":84,"meta":85,"style":85},"language-md shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","- Repository\n  - .git\n  - README.md\n  - package.json\n  - src\n    - components\n      - Button\n      - Input\n      - ...\n    - pages\n      - index\n      - shopping\n      - admin\n      - ...\n  - public\n  - ...其他檔案\n","md","",[56,87,88,101,110,118,126,134,143,152,160,168,176,184,192,200,207,215],{"__ignoreMap":85},[89,90,93,97],"span",{"class":91,"line":92},"line",1,[89,94,96],{"class":95},"syBk-","-",[89,98,100],{"class":99},"s8XSl"," Repository\n",[89,102,104,107],{"class":91,"line":103},2,[89,105,106],{"class":95},"  -",[89,108,109],{"class":99}," .git\n",[89,111,113,115],{"class":91,"line":112},3,[89,114,106],{"class":95},[89,116,117],{"class":99}," README.md\n",[89,119,121,123],{"class":91,"line":120},4,[89,122,106],{"class":95},[89,124,125],{"class":99}," package.json\n",[89,127,129,131],{"class":91,"line":128},5,[89,130,106],{"class":95},[89,132,133],{"class":99}," src\n",[89,135,137,140],{"class":91,"line":136},6,[89,138,139],{"class":95},"    -",[89,141,142],{"class":99}," components\n",[89,144,146,149],{"class":91,"line":145},7,[89,147,148],{"class":95},"      -",[89,150,151],{"class":99}," Button\n",[89,153,155,157],{"class":91,"line":154},8,[89,156,148],{"class":95},[89,158,159],{"class":99}," Input\n",[89,161,163,165],{"class":91,"line":162},9,[89,164,148],{"class":95},[89,166,167],{"class":99}," ...\n",[89,169,171,173],{"class":91,"line":170},10,[89,172,139],{"class":95},[89,174,175],{"class":99}," pages\n",[89,177,179,181],{"class":91,"line":178},11,[89,180,148],{"class":95},[89,182,183],{"class":99}," index\n",[89,185,187,189],{"class":91,"line":186},12,[89,188,148],{"class":95},[89,190,191],{"class":99}," shopping\n",[89,193,195,197],{"class":91,"line":194},13,[89,196,148],{"class":95},[89,198,199],{"class":99}," admin\n",[89,201,203,205],{"class":91,"line":202},14,[89,204,148],{"class":95},[89,206,167],{"class":99},[89,208,210,212],{"class":91,"line":209},15,[89,211,106],{"class":95},[89,213,214],{"class":99}," public\n",[89,216,218,220],{"class":91,"line":217},16,[89,219,106],{"class":95},[89,221,222],{"class":99}," ...其他檔案\n",[17,224,225],{},"透過上面架構我們可以看到會 Monolith 會是一個 Git 管理一整個專案。",[17,227,228],{},"雖然 Monolith 的架構非常方便也簡單，在做一些 MVP 專案是相當不錯的首選，可是也會有一些問題存在，當專案開始越來越大時，這個專案就會變得越來越難維護，為什麼呢？舉例來講，我們這個專案裡面可能有包含了以下幾個功能模組：",[46,230,231,234,237],{},[49,232,233],{},"前台首頁",[49,235,236],{},"前台購物頁面",[49,238,239],{},"後台管理\n...等等功能",[17,241,242],{},"開發以及部署的速度會隨著專案越來越龐大而變得越來越慢，就連一個小改動你都需要跑完一整個專案的編譯、測試、部署等等流程，而且只要一個地方出錯，這個專案就會跟你說一聲「掰掰」",[17,244,245],{},[69,246],{"alt":247,"src":248},"掰掰","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fmonorepo\u002Fim-leaving-leaving.gif",[17,250,251],{},"那麼為了解決這問題，我們就延伸出了另一個專案架構，也就是 Multi Repository。",[38,253,255],{"id":254},"multi-repository多個儲存庫","Multi Repository（多個儲存庫）",[17,257,258],{},"Multi Repository（後面簡稱 Multi）是什麼呢？簡單來講就是將原本的 Monolith 拆分成多個 Repository，也就是將原本的專案拆分成多個專案，每個專案都有自己的 Repository，這樣就可以讓每個專案獨立開發、獨立部署，這樣就可以解決 Monolith 的問題。",[17,260,261],{},"那麼這個專案架構就會從原本的 Monolith 變成以下的架構：",[80,263,265],{"className":82,"code":264,"language":84,"meta":85,"style":85},"- A Repository\n  - .git\n  - README.md\n  - package.json\n  - src\n    - components\n      - Button\n      - Input\n      - ...\n    - pages\n      - index\n      - ...\n  - public\n  - ...其他檔案\n- B Repository\n  - .git\n  - README.md\n  - package.json\n  - src\n    - components\n      - Button\n      - Input\n      - ...\n    - pages\n      - shopping\n      - ...\n  - public\n  - ...其他檔案\n- C Repository\n  - .git\n  - README.md\n  - package.json\n  - src\n    - components\n      - Button\n      - Input\n      - ...\n    - pages\n      - admin\n      - ...\n  - public\n  - ...其他檔案\n",[56,266,267,274,280,286,292,298,304,310,316,322,328,334,340,346,352,359,365,372,379,386,393,400,407,414,421,428,435,442,449,457,464,471,478,485,492,499,506,513,520,527,534,541],{"__ignoreMap":85},[89,268,269,271],{"class":91,"line":92},[89,270,96],{"class":95},[89,272,273],{"class":99}," A Repository\n",[89,275,276,278],{"class":91,"line":103},[89,277,106],{"class":95},[89,279,109],{"class":99},[89,281,282,284],{"class":91,"line":112},[89,283,106],{"class":95},[89,285,117],{"class":99},[89,287,288,290],{"class":91,"line":120},[89,289,106],{"class":95},[89,291,125],{"class":99},[89,293,294,296],{"class":91,"line":128},[89,295,106],{"class":95},[89,297,133],{"class":99},[89,299,300,302],{"class":91,"line":136},[89,301,139],{"class":95},[89,303,142],{"class":99},[89,305,306,308],{"class":91,"line":145},[89,307,148],{"class":95},[89,309,151],{"class":99},[89,311,312,314],{"class":91,"line":154},[89,313,148],{"class":95},[89,315,159],{"class":99},[89,317,318,320],{"class":91,"line":162},[89,319,148],{"class":95},[89,321,167],{"class":99},[89,323,324,326],{"class":91,"line":170},[89,325,139],{"class":95},[89,327,175],{"class":99},[89,329,330,332],{"class":91,"line":178},[89,331,148],{"class":95},[89,333,183],{"class":99},[89,335,336,338],{"class":91,"line":186},[89,337,148],{"class":95},[89,339,167],{"class":99},[89,341,342,344],{"class":91,"line":194},[89,343,106],{"class":95},[89,345,214],{"class":99},[89,347,348,350],{"class":91,"line":202},[89,349,106],{"class":95},[89,351,222],{"class":99},[89,353,354,356],{"class":91,"line":209},[89,355,96],{"class":95},[89,357,358],{"class":99}," B Repository\n",[89,360,361,363],{"class":91,"line":217},[89,362,106],{"class":95},[89,364,109],{"class":99},[89,366,368,370],{"class":91,"line":367},17,[89,369,106],{"class":95},[89,371,117],{"class":99},[89,373,375,377],{"class":91,"line":374},18,[89,376,106],{"class":95},[89,378,125],{"class":99},[89,380,382,384],{"class":91,"line":381},19,[89,383,106],{"class":95},[89,385,133],{"class":99},[89,387,389,391],{"class":91,"line":388},20,[89,390,139],{"class":95},[89,392,142],{"class":99},[89,394,396,398],{"class":91,"line":395},21,[89,397,148],{"class":95},[89,399,151],{"class":99},[89,401,403,405],{"class":91,"line":402},22,[89,404,148],{"class":95},[89,406,159],{"class":99},[89,408,410,412],{"class":91,"line":409},23,[89,411,148],{"class":95},[89,413,167],{"class":99},[89,415,417,419],{"class":91,"line":416},24,[89,418,139],{"class":95},[89,420,175],{"class":99},[89,422,424,426],{"class":91,"line":423},25,[89,425,148],{"class":95},[89,427,191],{"class":99},[89,429,431,433],{"class":91,"line":430},26,[89,432,148],{"class":95},[89,434,167],{"class":99},[89,436,438,440],{"class":91,"line":437},27,[89,439,106],{"class":95},[89,441,214],{"class":99},[89,443,445,447],{"class":91,"line":444},28,[89,446,106],{"class":95},[89,448,222],{"class":99},[89,450,452,454],{"class":91,"line":451},29,[89,453,96],{"class":95},[89,455,456],{"class":99}," C Repository\n",[89,458,460,462],{"class":91,"line":459},30,[89,461,106],{"class":95},[89,463,109],{"class":99},[89,465,467,469],{"class":91,"line":466},31,[89,468,106],{"class":95},[89,470,117],{"class":99},[89,472,474,476],{"class":91,"line":473},32,[89,475,106],{"class":95},[89,477,125],{"class":99},[89,479,481,483],{"class":91,"line":480},33,[89,482,106],{"class":95},[89,484,133],{"class":99},[89,486,488,490],{"class":91,"line":487},34,[89,489,139],{"class":95},[89,491,142],{"class":99},[89,493,495,497],{"class":91,"line":494},35,[89,496,148],{"class":95},[89,498,151],{"class":99},[89,500,502,504],{"class":91,"line":501},36,[89,503,148],{"class":95},[89,505,159],{"class":99},[89,507,509,511],{"class":91,"line":508},37,[89,510,148],{"class":95},[89,512,167],{"class":99},[89,514,516,518],{"class":91,"line":515},38,[89,517,139],{"class":95},[89,519,175],{"class":99},[89,521,523,525],{"class":91,"line":522},39,[89,524,148],{"class":95},[89,526,199],{"class":99},[89,528,530,532],{"class":91,"line":529},40,[89,531,148],{"class":95},[89,533,167],{"class":99},[89,535,537,539],{"class":91,"line":536},41,[89,538,106],{"class":95},[89,540,214],{"class":99},[89,542,544,546],{"class":91,"line":543},42,[89,545,106],{"class":95},[89,547,222],{"class":99},[17,549,550],{},"看起來這種專案架構是相當不錯的，讓我們解決了牽一髮而動全身的問題，而這個專案架構也會將功能模組各自拆分成一個專案，這樣就可以讓每個專案獨立開發、獨立部署，這樣就可以解決 Monolith 的問題。",[17,552,553],{},"但卻也有一些問題發生，我們在上面的例子中，我們可以看到 Button、Input 這兩個功能模組都是重複的，這樣就會造成重複開發的問題，而且當這兩個功能模組有一個地方出錯時，我們就需要到每個專案去修改，這樣就會造成維護上的困難，當然不只有這個問題存在，像是專案的 CI\u002FCD、套件的版本等等也就會變得更加難以維護 QAQ...",[17,555,556],{},[69,557],{"alt":558,"src":559},"崩潰","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fmonorepo\u002F202404140133.jpg",[38,561,563],{"id":562},"mono-repository單一儲存庫","Mono Repository（單一儲存庫）",[17,565,566],{},"那麼為了解決這個問題，所以又延伸出了另一個專案架構，也就是我們這一篇要說的重點 Monorepo 架構。",[17,568,569],{},"這時候應該有點混亂了，所以我決定畫圖來讓大家更加了解彼此的架構差異，首先是 Monolith：",[17,571,572],{},[69,573],{"alt":574,"src":575},"Monolith Repository","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fmonorepo\u002FMonolith%20Repository.png",[17,577,578],{},"我們可以看到 Monolith 的專案架構是一個專案一個 Repository，裡面通常會包含了許多功能模組，這樣就會造成牽一髮而動全身的問題。",[17,580,581],{},"接下來是 Multi：",[17,583,584],{},[69,585],{"alt":586,"src":587},"Multi Repository","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fmonorepo\u002FMulti%20Repository.png",[17,589,590],{},"我們可以看到 Multi 的專案架構是將原本的 Monolith 拆分成多個 Repository，這樣就可以讓每個專案獨立開發、獨立部署，這樣就可以解決 Monolith 的問題。",[17,592,593],{},"最後是 Mono Repository（後面簡稱 Monorepo）：",[17,595,596],{},[69,597],{"alt":598,"src":599},"Mono Repository","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fmonorepo\u002FMono%20Repository.png",[17,601,602],{},"透過圖像我們可以看到原本 Multi 都是獨立的 Git 管理，但是在 Monorepo 中，我們可以看到所有的專案都是在同一個 Repository 中並且由一個 Git 管理，這樣就可以解決 Multi 的問題，讓我們可以將所有的專案都放在同一個 Repository 中，讓所有的專案共享相同的資源。",[17,604,605],{},"雖然 Monorepo 的架構解決了 Multi 的問題，但也有一些缺點，例如...",[46,607,608,615,618,621],{},[49,609,610,611,614],{},"專案肥大後 ",[56,612,613],{},"git clone"," 時會花費較多時間",[49,616,617],{},"共用的東西必須要規劃好，否則容易互相影響",[49,619,620],{},"由於 Monorepo 中的專案都是共用的，所以無法區分專案的權限",[49,622,623],{},"Git 儲存庫的大小會變得非常大",[17,625,626],{},"我們可以發現不論是哪一種專案架構，都有屬於他的優缺點，所以在選擇專案架構時，可以評估一下自己的專案需求，再來選擇適合的專案架構。",[21,628,630],{"id":629},"用-vite-實作一個-monorepo","用 Vite 實作一個 Monorepo",[17,632,633],{},"接下來我將會介紹如何使用 Vite + pnpm 建立一個 Vue3 的 Monorepo，首先請你先依照以下步驟準備好環境：",[80,635,639],{"className":636,"code":637,"language":638,"meta":85,"style":85},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","mkdir monorepo-example-pnpm-vue3\ncd monorepo-example-pnpm-vue3\npnpm init\n","bash",[56,640,641,651,659],{"__ignoreMap":85},[89,642,643,647],{"class":91,"line":92},[89,644,646],{"class":645},"smYoP","mkdir",[89,648,650],{"class":649},"sWayO"," monorepo-example-pnpm-vue3\n",[89,652,653,657],{"class":91,"line":103},[89,654,656],{"class":655},"stw71","cd",[89,658,650],{"class":649},[89,660,661,664],{"class":91,"line":112},[89,662,663],{"class":645},"pnpm",[89,665,666],{"class":649}," init\n",[17,668,669,670,677],{},"接下來我們要做一點特別的設定，在 pnpm 的 ",[671,672,676],"a",{"href":673,"rel":674},"https:\u002F\u002Fpnpm.io\u002Fzh\u002Fworkspaces",[675],"nofollow","工作空間（Workspace）"," 官方文件有說到一件事情，如果我們要建立 Monorepo 的話會需要在根目錄建立一個「pnpm-workspace.yaml」檔案，所以請你在這個專案底下建立一個「pnpm-workspace.yaml」檔案。",[12,679,680],{"title":14,"type":15},[17,681,682,683,686],{},"pnpm-workspace.yaml 這個檔案主要是用來告訴 pnpm 這個專案是一個 Monorepo 專案，並且在你執行 ",[56,684,685],{},"pnpm install"," 時會自動安裝所有專案的相依套件",[17,688,689],{},"內容要寫什麼呢？這邊先讓我們回頭看一下 Monorepo 的圖：",[17,691,692],{},[69,693],{"alt":598,"src":599},[17,695,696],{},"我們可以看到一個 Git 底下會管理很多個專案，所以通常 Monorepo 的專案會長這樣：",[80,698,700],{"className":82,"code":699,"language":84,"meta":85,"style":85},"- Git\n  - pnpm-workspace.yaml\n  - package.json\n  - apps\n  - packages\n",[56,701,702,709,716,722,729],{"__ignoreMap":85},[89,703,704,706],{"class":91,"line":92},[89,705,96],{"class":95},[89,707,708],{"class":99}," Git\n",[89,710,711,713],{"class":91,"line":103},[89,712,106],{"class":95},[89,714,715],{"class":99}," pnpm-workspace.yaml\n",[89,717,718,720],{"class":91,"line":112},[89,719,106],{"class":95},[89,721,125],{"class":99},[89,723,724,726],{"class":91,"line":120},[89,725,106],{"class":95},[89,727,728],{"class":99}," apps\n",[89,730,731,733],{"class":91,"line":128},[89,732,106],{"class":95},[89,734,735],{"class":99}," packages\n",[17,737,738],{},"我們可以看到有一個 apps 資料夾，這個就是我們將會放置所有專案的地方，所以我們要在根目錄建立一個「apps」資料夾",[80,740,742],{"className":636,"code":741,"language":638,"meta":85,"style":85},"mkdir apps\n",[56,743,744],{"__ignoreMap":85},[89,745,746,748],{"class":91,"line":92},[89,747,646],{"class":645},[89,749,728],{"class":649},[17,751,752],{},"接著在「pnpm-workspace.yaml」檔案中寫入以下內容：",[80,754,758],{"className":755,"code":756,"language":757,"meta":85,"style":85},"language-yaml shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","packages:\n  - apps\u002F*\n","yaml",[56,759,760,769],{"__ignoreMap":85},[89,761,762,766],{"class":91,"line":92},[89,763,765],{"class":764},"syv7_","packages",[89,767,768],{"class":99},":\n",[89,770,771,774],{"class":91,"line":103},[89,772,773],{"class":99},"  - ",[89,775,776],{"class":649},"apps\u002F*\n",[17,778,779],{},"到這邊為止，已經將 Monorepo 的基本環境準備好了，接下來就是建立一個 Vue3 的專案，請你移動到「apps」資料夾中，並且建立一個 Vue3 的專案：",[80,781,783],{"className":636,"code":782,"language":638,"meta":85,"style":85},"cd apps\npnpm create vue@latest\n",[56,784,785,791],{"__ignoreMap":85},[89,786,787,789],{"class":91,"line":92},[89,